{
  "chapter": "064",
  "title": "司马穰苴列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "受命将兵",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马穰苴</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田完</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐景公</span>时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阿</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甄</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河上</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>退。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>为此担忧。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏婴</span>便举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田穰苴</span>说:\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>虽然是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶孽</span>，但他此人文能使众人归附，武能威慑敌人，望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主试用他。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>，与他谈论军事，非常高兴，任命他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，率兵去抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>之师。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>说:\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>一向卑贱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主把我从里巷之中提拔上来，加于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>之上，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>未归附，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不信服，人微权轻，希望能得到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宠臣</span>、国中所尊敬的人来担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">监军</span>，才行。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>答应了，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>前去。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "斩庄贾立威",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>辞别<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>后，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>约定说:\"明日<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日中</span>在军门相会。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>先驰往军中，立起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">表</span>木、设下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">漏</span>壶等候<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄贾\">贾（庄贾）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄贾\">贾（庄贾）</span>一向骄贵，认为统领的是自己的军队而自己又是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">监</span>军，不很着急；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>和近臣们为他饯行，留下来饮酒。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日中</span>时分而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄贾\">贾（庄贾）</span>还没到。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>就推倒<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">表</span>木、抛开<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">漏</span>壶，进入军中，巡视部队、整肃军纪，申明军令条约。军纪既已定下，到傍晚时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>才赶到。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>说:\"为什么迟到呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄贾\">贾（庄贾）</span>谢罪说:\"不才的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>们为我饯行，所以停留了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>说:\"将领受命的那天就要忘掉自己的家，面对军纪约束就要忘掉自己的亲人，拿起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">枹鼓</span>冲锋的紧急时刻就要忘掉自身。如今敌国深入侵犯，国内骚动不安，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>风吹日晒暴露在边境，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主寝不安席，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">食不甘味</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>的性命都系于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主一身，还说什么饯行！\"召来<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军正</span>问道:\"按<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">军法</span>，约定时间而晚到的该怎么处置？\"回答:\"<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>害怕了，派人飞马向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>报告，请求救援。使者去后还没回来，于是就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄贾</span>以示众于<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵都震惊战栗。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "斩仆徇军",
      "text": "过了一段时间，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄贾\">贾（庄贾）</span>，驰车闯入军中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>说:\"将领在军中，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主的命令有可以不接受的。\"问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军正</span>:\"在军中驰车，按<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">军法</span>该怎么处置？\"军正说:\"<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>十分恐惧。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>说:\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主的使者不可以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>。\"于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">仆</span>从，斫去<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>的左<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">驸</span>，斫去<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>的左<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">骖</span>，以示众于<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>。让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>回去报告，然后才出发。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "治军退敌",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>的住宿、井灶、饮食、病情、医药，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>都亲自过问抚慰。把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>的全部资粮都<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>来犒劳<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>，自己与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>平分粮食。他把那些瘦弱者与自己等同对待，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三天（时长）</span>之后才重新整饬部队。病患者都请求一起行动，争相奋勇为他赴<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>军听说后，因此<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">罢</span>兵而去。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军听说后，渡水<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">解</span>围而退。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追击</span>他们，收复了所失去的封内故境而引兵归国。"
    },
    "1.4": {
      "title": "尊为大司马",
      "text": "还未到国都，就解散部队，解除军纪约束，立誓盟而后入邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>与众<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>到郊外迎接，犒劳军队行完<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>仪，然后才回寝宫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>后，尊封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>一天天在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国更加尊贵。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "谗毁而死",
      "text": "不久<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>中<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">鲍氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高</span>氏、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">国</span>氏之类嫉害他，向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>进谗。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">退</span>斥<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马穰苴\">苴（司马穰苴）</span>发病而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田乞</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田豹</span>等人因此怨恨<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">国</span>等家族。此后到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田常</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简公</span>时，便全部<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">高子</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">国子</span>的<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>人。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田常\">常（田常）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">曾孙</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田和\">和（田和）</span>，便<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>，用兵行威，大多效法<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>的军法，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都来<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "司马兵法",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>追论古代<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，并把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>附于其中，因此号称<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">司马穰苴兵法</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我读<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">司马兵法</span>，宏阔深远，即使是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>的<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">征伐</span>，也未能完全尽显其义，如其文字辞采，也略显褒扬了。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>，区区为小国领兵，哪里顾得上<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">司马兵法</span>中的揖让之礼呢？世上已多有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">司马兵法</span>，因此不再论述，只著录<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>的列传。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河上</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>绩。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晏婴\">婴（晏婴）</span>荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>，武能威敌。<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄贾\">贾（庄贾）</span>徇军，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>惊惕。我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卒</span>强壮，彼<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寇</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">退</span>避固壁。军法见行于<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span>，实得益于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗戚</span>。"
    }
  }
}